this serum might just be that one for brightening and hydrating! 🌿🤍✨ just tried the SKIN1004 Madagascar Centella Tone Brightening Capsule Ampoule for the first time and omg! my skin felt instantly fresh and soothed 💧🤍

i’ll be using this for the next few weeks so I’ll def update y’all with the results! 🤍
